    <text class="white" id="introText" width="300" x="25" y="100"><![CDATA[  <p>Now we've given you an idea of the kind of work we do in Finance, let's take a closer look at each of our expert teams.</p>   <p class="prompt">Explore the Finance offices and select each room to find out how each team contributes to Mondelēz International's continued success.</p> ]]></text>

